queries.query: SELECT count(log_event_type) as "y_axis_1"  FROM "jumpcloud"  WHERE log_event_type IN ('login_attempt')
SELECT log_initiated_by_username as "x_axis_1", count(log_initiated_by_username) as "y_axis_1"  FROM "jumpcloud"  GROUP BY x_axis_1
SELECT log_geoip_latitude as latitude, log_geoip_longitude as longitude, count(log_initiated_by_username) as weight FROM "jumpcloud" GROUP BY latitude, longitude
SELECT log_geoip_country_code as "x_axis_1", count(log_geoip_country_code) as "y_axis_1"  FROM "jumpcloud"  GROUP BY x_axis_1
SELECT log_geoip_region_name as "x_axis_1", count(log_geoip_region_name) as "y_axis_1"  FROM "jumpcloud"  GROUP BY x_axis_1
SELECT log_geoip_timezone as "x_axis_1", count(log_geoip_timezone) as "y_axis_1"  FROM "jumpcloud"  GROUP BY x_axis_1
SELECT log_system_displayname as "x_axis_2"  FROM "jumpcloud"  GROUP BY x_axis_2
SELECT histogram(_timestamp) as "x_axis_1", count(log_timestamp) as "y_axis_1"  FROM "jumpcloud"  GROUP BY x_axis_1 ORDER BY x_axis_1 ASC
SELECT log_client_ip as "x_axis_1", log_message as "x_axis_2"  FROM "jumpcloud"  GROUP BY x_axis_1, x_axis_2

panels.title: Frequent IP Addresses for Login Attempts

queries.query: SELECT log_client_ip as "x_axis_1", count(log_client_ip) as "y_axis_1"  FROM "jumpcloud"  GROUP BY x_axis_1
SELECT log_username as "x_axis_1", count(log_username) as "y_axis_1"  FROM "jumpcloud"  GROUP BY x_axis_1

panels.title: System IDs with Multiple Login Attempts

queries.query: SELECT log_initiated_by_username as "x_axis_1", log_system_id as "x_axis_2", count(log_system_id) as "y_axis_1"  FROM "jumpcloud"  GROUP BY x_axis_1, x_axis_2
SELECT log_initiated_by_email as "x_axis_1", count(log_initiated_by_email) as "y_axis_1"  FROM "jumpcloud"  GROUP BY x_axis_1
SELECT log_system_hostname as "x_axis_2", log_application_name as "x_axis_3"  FROM "jumpcloud"  WHERE log_event_type IN ('software_remove')  GROUP BY x_axis_2, x_axis_3
SELECT log_system_hostname as "x_axis_2", log_application_name as "x_axis_3"  FROM "jumpcloud"  WHERE log_event_type IN ('software_add')  GROUP BY x_axis_2, x_axis_3
SELECT log_system_hostname as "x_axis_2", log_application_name as "x_axis_3"  FROM "jumpcloud"  WHERE log_event_type IN ('software_change')  GROUP BY x_axis_2, x_axis_3
